## Widgets
Everything in Flutter is a widget. `StatelessWidget` does not change. `StatefulWidget` can rebuild when state changes.
```dart
class MyText extends StatelessWidget {
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) => Text('Hello');
}
```

